(1768, 'en', 'Cx\\Modules\\Topics\\Model\\Entity\\Entry', 'description', '442', 'Indemnity insurance cover is provided if a financial loss is the prerequisite and criterion upon which the <a href="insurer">insurer</a>''s obligation to indemnify is evaluated.'),
