(1804, 'en', 'Cx\\Modules\\Topics\\Model\\Entity\\Entry', 'description', '451', 'Life insurance based on an individual tariff. Over the <a href="duration-of-a-contract-or-contractual-duration">duration of the contract</a> the savings part of the premium, including any interest due, forms the <a href="mathematical-or-policy-reserve">policy reserve</a> which is to be paid at the latest on the expiry of the contract.'),
